General.Name: Fram Skandinavien AB Series B
General.Description: Fram Skandinavien AB (publ) provides digital consultancy and professional services in Southeast Asia. The company offers SaaS, web app, mobile app, and eCommerce development services; and system performance optimization and DevOps managed services. It also provides a range of managed services across digital, development, cyber, and enterprise systems. The company was founded in 1893 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
